Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed occurring immediately after Plagiarism Originality Report Completed
Metric: Frequency of activity 'SW-Checklist Completed' for cases where activity 'Plagiarism Originality Report Completed' occurs

Name: Percentage of process variants that include SW-Checklist Completed before transitioning to SW-Awaiting AE Assignment
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Number of times SW-Checklist Completed appears in variants that eventually lead to SW-EIC Reject
Metric: Number of 'SW-Checklist Completed' activities for cases where activity 'SW-EIC Reject' occurs

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed relative to SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion across all cases
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Number of SW-Checklist Completed occurrences in cases that also include Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: Number of 'SW-Checklist Completed' activities for cases where activity 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission' occurs

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed that directly precedes SW-Awaiting AE Assignment compared to other downstream activities
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'SW-Awaiting AE Assignment'

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed in variants with performance duration below the median case duration
Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed executions performed by SYSTEM versus other performers (though all appear to be SYSTEM, this validates consistency)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Ratio of SW-Checklist Completed to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation across the entire log
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Percentage of process instances where SW-Checklist Completed occurs only once, indicating no re-submission or re-checking
Metric: the average of the function base == 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Checklist Completed'

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed activities that occur within 24 hours of SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion
Metric: the average of the function base < 24 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Checklist Completed' filtered by the function ma > 0 where ma is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Awaiting Checklist Completion'

Name: Percentage of SW-Checklist Completed executions that are not followed by any checklist reminder activities (e.g., SW-Checklist Completion is due in three days or SW-Checklist Completion now due)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Percentage of variants containing SW-Checklist Completed that proceed to reviewer assignment activities (e.g., SW-Initial Reviewer Selection or SW-AE Assign Reviewers)
Metric: Percentage of 'SW-Checklist Completed' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of SW-Checklist Completed in variants that eventually reach a final editorial decision (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Major Revision)
Metric: the average of the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'SW-Checklist Completed'
